  <bioghist id="aspace_6bb36f014fc63938a152baf48e184b5b">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>John Burchard attended Deep Springs College between 1928 - 1930. He resided at Telluride House 1931 - 1934.</p>  </bioghist>
